{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1084,"text":"Like many of us,"},{"time":2818,"text":"I've had several careers in my life,"},{"time":5214,"text":"and although they've been varied,"},{"time":7389,"text":"my first job set the foundation\nfor all of them."},{"time":11300,"text":"I was a home-birth midwife\nthroughout my 20s."},{"time":15623,"text":"Delivering babies taught me\nvaluable and sometimes surprising things,"},{"time":20771,"text":"like how to start a car at 2am."},{"time":23565,"text":"when it's 10 degrees below zero."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25387,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":26412,"text":"Or how to revive a father\nwho's fainted at the sight of blood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30771,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":31846,"text":"Or how to cut the umbilical cord just so,"},{"time":34316,"text":"to make a beautiful belly button."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36561,"text":"But those aren't the things\nthat stuck with me or guided me"},{"time":40370,"text":"when I stopped being a midwife\nand started other jobs."},{"time":44378,"text":"What stuck with me was this bedrock belief"},{"time":48495,"text":"that each one of us comes into this world\nwith a unique worth."},{"time":54282,"text":"When I looked into the face of a newborn,"},{"time":58192,"text":"I caught a glimpse of that worthiness,"},{"time":61909,"text":"that sense of unapologetic selfhood,"},{"time":64775,"text":"that unique spark."},{"time":68586,"text":"I use the word \"soul\"\nto describe that spark,"},{"time":72367,"text":"because it's the only word in English\nthat comes close to naming"},{"time":77030,"text":"what each baby brought into the room."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80623,"text":"Every newborn was as singular\nas a snowflake,"},{"time":85315,"text":"a matchless mash-up of biology"},{"time":88710,"text":"and ancestry and mystery."},{"time":91914,"text":"And then that baby grows up,"},{"time":94055,"text":"and in order to fit into the family,"},{"time":96194,"text":"to conform to the culture,"},{"time":98259,"text":"to the community, to the gender,"},{"time":101174,"text":"that little one begins to cover its soul,"},{"time":104140,"text":"layer by layer."},{"time":106197,"text":"We're born this way,"},{"time":108405,"text":"but --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":109587,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":111203,"text":"But as we grow, a lot\nof things happen to us"},{"time":114640,"text":"that make us ..."},{"time":117815,"text":"want to hide our soulful\neccentricities and authenticity."},{"time":122983,"text":"We've all done this."},{"time":124374,"text":"Everyone in this room is a former baby --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":127237,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":128283,"text":"with a distinctive birthright."},{"time":131560,"text":"But as adults, we spend so much\nof our time uncomfortable in our own skin,"},{"time":136800,"text":"like we have ADD:\nauthenticity deficit disorder."},{"time":141449,"text":"But not those babies --"},{"time":143081,"text":"not yet."},{"time":144347,"text":"Their message to me was:"},{"time":146453,"text":"uncover your soul"},{"time":148728,"text":"and look for that soul-spark"},{"time":151945,"text":"in everyone else."},{"time":153179,"text":"It's still there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155172,"text":"And here's what I learned\nfrom laboring women."},{"time":158414,"text":"Their message was about staying open,"},{"time":161438,"text":"even when things are painful."},{"time":164584,"text":"A woman's cervix normally looks like this."},{"time":167036,"text":"It's a tight little muscle"},{"time":169210,"text":"at the base of the uterus."},{"time":171243,"text":"And during labor,\nit has to stretch from this"},{"time":175576,"text":"to this."},{"time":176982,"text":"Ouch!"},{"time":178269,"text":"If you fight against that pain,"},{"time":181343,"text":"you just create more pain,"},{"time":183051,"text":"and you block what wants to be born."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186482,"text":"I'll never forget the magic\nthat would happen"},{"time":190344,"text":"when a woman stopped resisting the pain"},{"time":194185,"text":"and opened."},{"time":195496,"text":"It was as if the forces\nof the universe took notice"},{"time":199211,"text":"and sent in a wave of help."},{"time":201973,"text":"I never forgot that message,"},{"time":203919,"text":"and now, when difficult\nor painful things happen to me"},{"time":207963,"text":"in my life or my work,"},{"time":209909,"text":"of course at first I resist them,"},{"time":212561,"text":"but then I remember\nwhat I learned from the mothers:"},{"time":215809,"text":"stay open."},{"time":217508,"text":"Stay curious."},{"time":218961,"text":"Ask the pain what it's come to deliver."},{"time":222017,"text":"Something new wants to be born."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225311,"text":"And there was one more big soulful lesson,"},{"time":227633,"text":"and that one I learned\nfrom Albert Einstein."},{"time":230769,"text":"He wasn't at any of the births, but --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":232749,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":233805,"text":"It was a lesson about time."},{"time":237732,"text":"At the end of his life,\nAlbert Einstein concluded"},{"time":241909,"text":"that our normal, hamster-wheel\nexperience of life"},{"time":246083,"text":"is an illusion."},{"time":247843,"text":"We run round and round, faster and faster,"},{"time":250260,"text":"trying to get somewhere."},{"time":252455,"text":"And all the while,"},{"time":255218,"text":"underneath surface time\nis this whole other dimension"},{"time":259288,"text":"where the past and the present\nand the future merge"},{"time":264367,"text":"and become deep time."},{"time":267414,"text":"And there's nowhere to get to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270716,"text":"Albert Einstein called\nthis state, this dimension,"},{"time":275089,"text":"\"only being.\""},{"time":276774,"text":"And he said when he experienced it,"},{"time":278754,"text":"he knew sacred awe."},{"time":281818,"text":"When I was delivering babies,"},{"time":283491,"text":"I was forced off the hamster wheel."},{"time":285410,"text":"Sometimes I had to sit for days,\nhours and hours,"},{"time":289213,"text":"just breathing with the parents;"},{"time":291823,"text":"just being."},{"time":293659,"text":"And I got a big dose of sacred awe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297156,"text":"So those are the three lessons\nI took with me from midwifery."},{"time":302253,"text":"One: uncover your soul."},{"time":305376,"text":"Two: when things get difficult\nor painful, try to stay open."},{"time":311568,"text":"And three: every now and then,\nstep off your hamster wheel"},{"time":315928,"text":"into deep time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318946,"text":"Those lessons have served me\nthroughout my life,"},{"time":322855,"text":"but they really served me recently,"},{"time":325338,"text":"when I took on the most\nimportant job of my life thus far."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330572,"text":"Two years ago, my younger sister\ncame out of remission"},{"time":334962,"text":"from a rare blood cancer,"},{"time":337719,"text":"and the only treatment left for her\nwas a bone marrow transplant."},{"time":342708,"text":"And against the odds,\nwe found a match for her,"},{"time":345821,"text":"who turned out to be me."},{"time":348794,"text":"I come from a family of four girls,"},{"time":352075,"text":"and when my sisters found out that\nI was my sister's perfect genetic match,"},{"time":358512,"text":"their reaction was, \"Really? You?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":360866,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":362273,"text":"\"A perfect match for her?\""},{"time":364453,"text":"Which is pretty typical for siblings."},{"time":367488,"text":"In a sibling society,\nthere's lots of things."},{"time":370221,"text":"There's love and there's friendship\nand there's protection."},{"time":374442,"text":"But there's also jealousy"},{"time":376603,"text":"and competition"},{"time":378600,"text":"and rejection and attack."},{"time":381867,"text":"In siblinghood, that's where we start\nassembling many of those first layers"},{"time":387829,"text":"that cover our soul."}]},{"cues":[{"time":390106,"text":"When I discovered I was my sister's match,"},{"time":393133,"text":"I went into research mode."},{"time":395194,"text":"And I discovered that"},{"time":398028,"text":"the premise of transplants\nis pretty straightforward."},{"time":400786,"text":"You destroy all the bone marrow\nin the cancer patient"},{"time":404070,"text":"with massive doses of chemotherapy,"},{"time":407293,"text":"and then you replace that marrow"},{"time":409727,"text":"with several million healthy\nmarrow cells from a donor."},{"time":413937,"text":"And then you do everything you can"},{"time":415767,"text":"to make sure that those new cells\nengraft in the patient."},{"time":420076,"text":"I also learned that bone marrow\ntransplants are fraught with danger."},{"time":425468,"text":"If my sister made it\nthrough the near-lethal chemotherapy,"},{"time":430734,"text":"she still would face other challenges."},{"time":433942,"text":"My cells"},{"time":436863,"text":"might attack her body."},{"time":439843,"text":"And her body might reject my cells."},{"time":442846,"text":"They call this rejection or attack,"},{"time":445315,"text":"and both could kill her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447583,"text":"Rejection. Attack."},{"time":450091,"text":"Those words had a familiar ring"},{"time":452306,"text":"in the context of being siblings."},{"time":455843,"text":"My sister and I had\na long history of love,"},{"time":458676,"text":"but we also had a long history\nof rejection and attack,"},{"time":462487,"text":"from minor misunderstandings\nto bigger betrayals."},{"time":467172,"text":"We didn't have\nthe kind of the relationship"},{"time":469330,"text":"where we talked about the deeper stuff;"},{"time":471887,"text":"but, like many siblings and like people\nin all kinds of relationships,"},{"time":476987,"text":"we were hesitant to tell our truths,"},{"time":479965,"text":"to reveal our wounds,"},{"time":482867,"text":"to admit our wrongdoings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":485180,"text":"But when I learned about\nthe dangers of rejection or attack,"},{"time":490095,"text":"I thought, it's time to change this."},{"time":493073,"text":"What if we left the bone marrow\ntransplant up to the doctors,"},{"time":497913,"text":"but did something that we later came\nto call our \"soul marrow transplant?\""},{"time":504205,"text":"What if we faced any pain\nwe had caused each other,"},{"time":508215,"text":"and instead of rejection or attack,"},{"time":511454,"text":"could we listen?"},{"time":513272,"text":"Could we forgive?"},{"time":515116,"text":"Could we merge?"},{"time":516580,"text":"Would that teach our cells to do the same?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":521431,"text":"To woo my skeptical sister,\nI turned to my parents' holy text:"},{"time":526268,"text":"the New Yorker Magazine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":527893,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":529833,"text":"I sent her a cartoon from its pages"},{"time":533428,"text":"as a way of explaining\nwhy we should visit a therapist"},{"time":537077,"text":"before having my bone marrow harvested\nand transplanted into her body."},{"time":542467,"text":"Here it is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":543736,"text":"\"I have never forgiven him for that thing\nI made up in my head.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":547874,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":550305,"text":"I told my sister"},{"time":552950,"text":"we had probably been doing the same thing,"},{"time":555811,"text":"carting around made-up stories\nin our heads that kept us separate."},{"time":562184,"text":"And I told her that after the transplant,"},{"time":565100,"text":"all of the blood flowing in her veins"},{"time":567718,"text":"would be my blood,"},{"time":569223,"text":"made from my marrow cells,"},{"time":572301,"text":"and that inside the nucleus\nof each of those cells"},{"time":576554,"text":"is a complete set of my DNA."},{"time":579351,"text":"\"I will be swimming around in you\nfor the rest of your life,\""},{"time":582755,"text":"I told my slightly horrified sister."}]},{"cues":[{"time":585538,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":587742,"text":"\"I think we better clean up\nour relationship.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":592168,"text":"A health crisis makes people\ndo all sorts of risky things,"},{"time":595512,"text":"like quitting a job\nor jumping out of an airplane"},{"time":599603,"text":"and, in the case of my sister,"},{"time":601618,"text":"saying \"yes\" to several therapy sessions,"},{"time":605723,"text":"during which we got down to the marrow."},{"time":611588,"text":"We looked at and released years of stories"},{"time":616005,"text":"and assumptions about each other"},{"time":618110,"text":"and blame and shame"},{"time":620212,"text":"until all that was left was love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":626175,"text":"People have said I was brave\nto undergo the bone marrow harvest,"},{"time":630387,"text":"but I don't think so."},{"time":632100,"text":"What felt brave to me"},{"time":634214,"text":"was that other kind\nof harvest and transplant,"},{"time":637423,"text":"the soul marrow transplant,"},{"time":639772,"text":"getting emotionally naked\nwith another human being,"},{"time":643774,"text":"putting aside pride and defensiveness,"},{"time":647267,"text":"lifting the layers"},{"time":649559,"text":"and sharing with each other\nour vulnerable souls."},{"time":654416,"text":"I called on those midwife lessons:"},{"time":657239,"text":"uncover your soul."},{"time":659963,"text":"Open to what's scary and painful."},{"time":662628,"text":"Look for the sacred awe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":665872,"text":"Here I am with my marrow cells\nafter the harvest."},{"time":669161,"text":"That's they call it -- \"harvest,\""},{"time":671085,"text":"like it's some kind of bucolic\nfarm-to-table event --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":674309,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":675491,"text":"Which I can assure you it is not."},{"time":679522,"text":"And here is my brave, brave sister"},{"time":682881,"text":"receiving my cells."},{"time":685768,"text":"After the transplant, we began to spend\nmore and more time together."},{"time":690289,"text":"It was as if we were little girls again."},{"time":693537,"text":"The past and the present merged."},{"time":696529,"text":"We entered deep time."},{"time":699331,"text":"I left the hamster wheel of work and life"},{"time":703631,"text":"to join my sister"},{"time":705992,"text":"on that lonely island"},{"time":708444,"text":"of illness and healing."},{"time":710948,"text":"We spent months together --"},{"time":712815,"text":"in the isolation unit,"},{"time":714601,"text":"in the hospital and in her home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":718411,"text":"Our fast-paced society"},{"time":720124,"text":"does not support or even value\nthis kind of work."},{"time":725308,"text":"We see it as a disruption\nof real life and important work."},{"time":729426,"text":"We worry about the emotional drain\nand the financial cost --"},{"time":733678,"text":"and, yes, there is a financial cost."},{"time":737277,"text":"But I was paid"},{"time":739590,"text":"in the kind of currency our culture\nseems to have forgotten all about."},{"time":745132,"text":"I was paid in love."},{"time":747629,"text":"I was paid in soul."},{"time":749398,"text":"I was paid in my sister."}]},{"cues":[{"time":752792,"text":"My sister said the year after transplant\nwas the best year of her life,"},{"time":758008,"text":"which was surprising."},{"time":759281,"text":"She suffered so much."},{"time":762364,"text":"But she said life never tasted as sweet,"},{"time":766004,"text":"and that because of the soul-baring"},{"time":768772,"text":"and the truth-telling\nwe had done with each other,"},{"time":771721,"text":"she became more unapologetically herself"},{"time":775561,"text":"with everyone."},{"time":776976,"text":"She said things\nshe'd always needed to say."},{"time":779968,"text":"She did things she always wanted to do."},{"time":783263,"text":"The same happened for me."},{"time":785246,"text":"I became braver about being authentic\nwith the people in my life."},{"time":791917,"text":"I said my truths,"},{"time":793634,"text":"but more important than that,\nI sought the truth of others."}]},{"cues":[{"time":799713,"text":"It wasn't until\nthe final chapter of this story"},{"time":803121,"text":"that I realized just how well\nmidwifery had trained me."},{"time":807214,"text":"After that best year of my sister's life,"},{"time":810153,"text":"the cancer came roaring back,"},{"time":812702,"text":"and this time there was nothing more\nthe doctors could do."},{"time":815998,"text":"They gave her just\na couple of months to live."}]},{"cues":[{"time":820196,"text":"The night before my sister died,"},{"time":823163,"text":"I sat by her bedside."},{"time":825895,"text":"She was so small and thin."},{"time":828766,"text":"I could see the blood pulsing in her neck."},{"time":831869,"text":"It was my blood, her blood, our blood."},{"time":836462,"text":"When she died, part of me would die, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":840687,"text":"I tried to make sense of it all,"},{"time":845383,"text":"how becoming one with each other"},{"time":848008,"text":"had made us more ourselves,"},{"time":850041,"text":"our soul selves,"},{"time":852249,"text":"and how by facing and opening\nto the pain of our past,"},{"time":857466,"text":"we'd finally been delivered to each other,"},{"time":860651,"text":"and how by stepping out of time,"},{"time":862925,"text":"we would now be connected forever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":866980,"text":"My sister left me with so many things,"},{"time":870365,"text":"and I'm going to leave you now\nwith just one of them."},{"time":873565,"text":"You don't have to wait\nfor a life-or-death situation"},{"time":878497,"text":"to clean up the relationships\nthat matter to you,"},{"time":881640,"text":"to offer the marrow of your soul"},{"time":885157,"text":"and to seek it in another."},{"time":888297,"text":"We can all do this."},{"time":890239,"text":"We can be like a new kind\nof first responder,"},{"time":895106,"text":"like the one to take\nthe first courageous step"},{"time":899906,"text":"toward the other,"},{"time":901682,"text":"and to do something or try to do something"},{"time":904951,"text":"other than rejection or attack."},{"time":908545,"text":"We can do this with our siblings"},{"time":910735,"text":"and our mates"},{"time":912161,"text":"and our friends and our colleagues."},{"time":914441,"text":"We can do this with the disconnection"},{"time":917093,"text":"and the discord all around us."},{"time":920410,"text":"We can do this for the soul of the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":924629,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":925844,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}